media.headline: McCullers Jr. K's Cruz
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: McCullers Jr. retires Cruz swinging
media.bigblurb: Lance McCullers Jr. forces Nelson Cruz to go down swinging for the third out in the top of the 1st inning

media.headline: Altuve out at first after review
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: Altuve out at first after review
media.bigblurb: Jose Altuve reaches on a single after he beats Jean Segura's throw, but the call is overturned after the Mariners challenge in the 1st

media.headline: McCann's solo homer
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: McCann opens scoring with a solo shot
media.bigblurb: Brian McCann drills a line drive over the left-field wall for a solo home run that puts the Astros up 1-0 in the bottom of the 3rd inning

media.headline: Zunino catches Springer stealing
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: Zunino nabs Springer trying to steal second
media.bigblurb: George Springer attempts to swipe a bag, but Mike Zunino throws down to second base to cut off the attempt for the third out of the inning

media.headline: Valencia brings home Haniger
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: Valencia ties game with RBI infield single
media.bigblurb: Danny Valencia hits a slow chopper to third base and reaches safely without a throw, allowing Mitch Haniger to score and tying the game at 1

media.headline: Iwakuma induces DP
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: Iwakuma forces McCann into inning-ending DP
media.bigblurb: Brian McCann hits a ground ball to Danny Valencia, who starts a 3-5-3 double play to end the bottom of the 5th inning

media.headline: McCullers Jr.'s handshake line
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: McCullers Jr. greets team prior to start
media.bigblurb: Lance McCullers Jr. goes down the dugout giving unique handshakes to each teammate he passes

media.headline: McCullers Jr. robs Dyson
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: McCullers Jr. makes unassisted play
media.bigblurb: Jarrod Dyson hits a slow chopper to the right side, but Lance McCullers Jr. uses his momentum to scoop the ball and run to first for the out

media.headline: Gonzalez's opposite-field homer
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: Gonzalez gives Astros lead with solo dinger
media.bigblurb: Martin Gonzalez lifts a fly ball over the left-field fence to give the Astros a 2-1 in the bottom of the 6th inning

media.headline: Giles K's Haniger to earn save
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: Giles fans Haniger to seal the game
media.bigblurb: Ken Giles gets Mitch Haniger to strike out on a check swing, stranding a runner on second and notching the save in the top of the 9th inning

media.headline: Zunino catches Springer again
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: Zunino tosses out a hesitant Springer
media.bigblurb: George Springer stops halfway on a steal attempt, allowing Mike Zunino to throw down and get the out for the second time of the game

media.headline: McCullers' strong outing
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: McCullers fans seven through six innings
media.bigblurb: Lance McCullers Jr. allows five hits and two walks while striking out seven in six innings of work during his first start of the season

media.headline: Servais on loss to Astros
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: Servais on impatience at plate in loss
media.bigblurb: Mariners manager Scott Servais talks about chasing pitches out of the zone and the strength of the Astros' bullpen in a loss to Houston

media.headline: Hinch on win over Mariners
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: Hinch on victory over the Mariners
media.bigblurb: A.J. Hinch talks about Lance McCullers' Jr.'s performance today and how important his bullpen is for future success

media.headline: McCann, McCullers Jr. on win
media.blurb: SEA@HOU: McCann, McCullers Jr. on win over Mariners
media.bigblurb: Brian McCann and Lance McCullers Jr. discuss their performances in the Astros' win over the Mariners

media.headline: Recap: SEA 1, HOU 2
media.blurb: 4/4/17: McCullers Jr. leads Astros to 2-1 win
media.bigblurb: Daily Recap: Lance McCullers Jr. fanned seven Mariners through six innings while Brian McCann and Marwin Gonzalez each homered in a 2-1 win
